AppSec+ is an application security software
AppSec+ API follows OpenAPI 3.0

AppSec+ has the following API Resource Groups (Top level domains of functionality in API):

1. Authentication
2. Applications
3. Scans
4. Vulnerabilities
5. Policies
6. Connectors
7. Identity Groups
8. Roles
9. Audit logs
10. Webhooks


Check the API file:
- Download the JSON file or Yaml file from the repo
- Go to https://editor.swagger.io/ 
- Click File> Import URL > https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ashokchandru/AppSec/refs/heads/main/appsec_plus_openapi_full.json
- Note: Regular Github url is an HTML file, to import API you need to give url to the raw file. Get link to the raw file from the top-right of the Github window
- You can see the list of API endpoints under default tag
